default7)
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultReporting to SHOT was initially voluntary but is now required by several professional bodies
default (Clinical Pathology Accreditation, Nursing and Midwifery Council)
default and is mandatory for clinicians in line with the General Medical Council’s  standard for Good Medical Practice
default, and the Francis Report
default.  
