default10)
default&#xa0; 
defaultOverall, about half of all reported events are a result of mistakes. 
defaultMost of these do not result in serious consequences for the patient.
default Each year the report includes learning points and recommendations for changes in practice.  
defaultSHOT
default reporting has been instrumental in changing practice both at the Blood 
defaultServic
defaultes and in hospital
default laboratories and clinical areas
default. 
default  
defaultSHOT
default thus alerts the NHS to transfusion safety issues which can be addressed in order to reduce the risks.
