default18)
default&#xa0; 
defaultMistakes occur because at every stage of the transfusion process the professionals involved do not 
defaultalways 
defaultfollow established procedures. This has been highlighted in 
defaultSHOT
default reports and the recommendation made for a checklist to be used.
default  This has not yet been widely adopted but is likely to improve safety of the key steps as has been demonstrated 
defaultby introduction of the WHO checklist 
defaultfor surgery.
